rough its us legend cars international subsidiary and produces and broadcasts syndicated motorsports programming to radio stations nationwide though its performance racing network subsidiary history since the early days in  when speedway motorsports inc executive chairman o bruton smith began construction of charlotte motor speedway speedway motorsports has developed a robust history of innovation and improvement to the race experience enjoyed by our fans sponsors team owners drivers media and others for nearly six decades speedway motorsports has built and modernized our eight worldclass motorsports properties to become the finest in the industry offering unmatched spectator enjoyment convenience and accessibility speedway motorsports provides souvenir merchandising services through its smi properties subsidiaries manufactures and distributes smallerscale modified racing cars and parts through its us legend cars international subsidiary and produces and broadcasts syndicated motorsports programming to radio stations nationwide though its performance racing network subsidiary      charlotte motor speedway was designed and built in  by current chairman o bruton smith the late curtis turner one of stock car racing’s earliest driving stars was smith’s business partner close  the inaugural world  nascar grand national series event was run on june   at charlotte motor speedway it was nascar”s first  mile race and it was the longest nascar race distance in terms of miles joe lee johnson was the winner of the inaugural race close  bruton smith takes over as chief executive close  performance racing network is formed close      first sports facility in america to offer yearround living with  condominiums close  the speedway club opens an exclusive dining and entertainment facility trackside at charlotte motor speedway close  acquired atlanta motor speedway close  lights are added to charlotte motor speedway to host first nascar night race on may   considered one of the most memorable moments in nascar allstar race history this race is better known as one hot night close      us legend cars international inc is launched providing fun and affordable “spec” class racing for anyone close  speedway motorsports is incorporated close  publicly traded on the new york stock exchange close  acquired bristol motor speedway close      acquired sonoma raceway close  texas motor speedway opens and hosts largest sporting event in texas history close  naming rights at cms sold to lowe’s companies inc close  acquired las vegas motor speedway close      acquired new hampshire motor speedway close  first fourlane dragway in the united states close  acquired kentucky speedway close  speedway tv becomes worlds largest hdtv at charlotte motor speedway close      sonoma raceway installed  solar panels close  big hoss tv becomes the new worlds largest hdtv at texas motor speedway close  battle at bristol – college football’s biggest game ever between virginia tech hokies and tennessee volunteers close  colossus is installed at bristol motor speedway colossus is the largest outdoor suspended digital display in the world close   o bruton smith inducted into nascar hall of fame close   speedway motorsports inc httpwwwspeedwaymotorsportscom privacy policy dedicated server provided by hosted solutions smi speedways atlanta motor speedway bristol motor speedway charlotte motor speedway kentucky speedway las vegas motor speedway new hampshire motor speedway sonoma raceway texas motor speedway other properties performance racing network smi properties us legend cars international speedway motorsports inc  nysetrk  stock quote  news  thestreet action alerts plus access aapjim cramers best stocks for charitable trust portfoliomost recent trade alert investing rules trading commandments real money access rm rules of investingjim cramers best stocks for  commandmentsstressed out stockscramers blog cramer mad money etfs futures markets much more banksbiotechretailtechper